  <summary>1/25/2007--Introduced.
Amends the Internal Revenue Code to treat certain controlled foreign corporations created or organized under the laws of a tax-haven country as domestic corporations for tax purposes. Sets forth a list of "tax-haven countries" and grants the Secretary of the Treasury authority to remove or add a country from such list.</summary>
